title: Ballville The Beginning  Games !!!
description:
The spaceship of travelling orbees crashed down on an unknown, uncharted planet. Could this magnificent world become a new home for the Orbs? Help the Captain find lost crew members and build a city from scratch in this innovative Match 3 game. Complete levels, solve interactive Hidden Objects and play enthralling mini-games. Use the abilities of each orb wisely in order to reach your goals. Find out curious details about the Orb folk in Orbopedia. Join the Orbs in their daring adventures and discover a new, spectacular world!
